[
  {
    "startTime": 9.9,
    "endTime": 13.100000000000001,
    "text": "I really felt quite distressed at not receiving an invitation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.1,
    "endTime": 15.1,
    "text": "You weren't wanted."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.2,
    "endTime": 16.599999999999998,
    "text": "Not wan⏤"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.1,
    "endTime": 21.3,
    "text": "Oh, dear, what an awkward situation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.4,
    "endTime": 24.099999999999998,
    "text": "I had hoped it was merely due to some oversight."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.9,
    "endTime": 27.7,
    "text": "Well, in that event, I'd best be on my way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.8,
    "endTime": 31.3,
    "text": "And... you're not offended, Your Excellency?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.6,
    "endTime": 34.2,
    "text": "Why, no, Your Majesty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.3,
    "endTime": 41.699999999999996,
    "text": "And to show I bear no ill will, I, too, shall bestow a gift on the child."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.4,
    "endTime": 56.9,
    "text": "Listen well, all of you. The princess shall, indeed, grow in grace and beauty, beloved by all who know her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.7,
    "endTime": 70.4,
    "text": "But... before the sun sets on her 16th birthday, she shall prick her finger on the spindle of a spinning wheel and die!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.5,
    "endTime": 72.0,
    "text": "Oh, no!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.2,
    "endTime": 75.2,
    "text": "Seize that creature!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.3,
    "endTime": 77.7,
    "text": "Stand back, you fool!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.1,
    "endTime": 88.6,
    "text": "Get the lamp!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.0,
    "endTime": 91.3,
    "text": "No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.4,
    "endTime": 95.4,
    "text": "Uh, uh, uh, Princess. Your time is up!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.5,
    "endTime": 99.4,
    "text": "Jasmine!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.8,
    "endTime": 103.7,
    "text": "Oh, nice shot, Jaf⏤"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.1,
    "endTime": 106.89999999999999,
    "text": "Don't toy with me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.6,
    "endTime": 109.6,
    "text": "Abu!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.7,
    "endTime": 113.0,
    "text": "Things are unraveling fast now, boy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.9,
    "endTime": 117.60000000000001,
    "text": "Get the point?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.4,
    "endTime": 125.80000000000001,
    "text": "I'm just getting warmed up!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.2,
    "endTime": 132.2,
    "text": "Are you afraid to fight me yourself, you cowardly snake?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.5,
    "endTime": 134.7,
    "text": "A snake, am I?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.0,
    "endTime": 139.9,
    "text": "Perhaps you'd like to see how snake-like I can be!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.2,
    "endTime": 152.7,
    "text": "- Mother⏤  - We're going home, Rapunzel. Now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.8,
    "endTime": 154.60000000000002,
    "text": "You... you don't understand."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.7,
    "endTime": 159.2,
    "text": "I've been on this incredible journey, and I've seen and learned so much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.3,
    "endTime": 161.3,
    "text": "I... I even met someone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.4,
    "endTime": 163.6,
    "text": "Yes. The wanted thief. I'm so proud."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.7,
    "endTime": 164.7,
    "text": "Come on, Rapunzel."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.8,
    "endTime": 166.10000000000002,
    "text": "Mother, wait!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.2,
    "endTime": 167.2,
    "text": "I think..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.1,
    "endTime": 170.7,
    "text": "I think he likes me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.8,
    "endTime": 173.8,
    "text": "Likes you? Please, Rapunzel, that's demented."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.9,
    "endTime": 176.9,
    "text": "- But Mother, I⏤  - This is why you never should have left."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.6,
    "endTime": 185.7,
    "text": "Dear, this whole romance that you've invented just proves you're too naive to be here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.8,
    "endTime": 189.3,
    "text": "Why would he like you? Come on now, really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.4,
    "endTime": 192.3,
    "text": "Look at you. You'll think that he's impressed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.1,
    "endTime": 196.7,
    "text": "Don't be a dummy; come with Mummy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.7,
    "endTime": 199.1,
    "text": "♪ Mother ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.2,
    "endTime": 200.1,
    "text": "No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.2,
    "endTime": 202.5,
    "text": "No?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.5,
    "endTime": 207.7,
    "text": "Oh. I see how it is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.9,
    "endTime": 213.6,
    "text": "Yes, hurry home, Princess."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.7,
    "endTime": 218.89999999999998,
    "text": "We wouldn't want to miss old Daddy's celebration, now, would we?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.0,
    "endTime": 222.4,
    "text": "Ha! Celebration indeed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.5,
    "endTime": 224.1,
    "text": "Oh, bah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.2,
    "endTime": 232.2,
    "text": "In my day, we had fantastical feasts when I lived in the palace."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.8,
    "endTime": 249.5,
    "text": "And now, look at me; wasted away to practically nothing, banished and exiled and practically starving while he and his flimsy fish-folk celebrate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.6,
    "endTime": 254.4,
    "text": "Well, I'll give 'em something to celebrate soon enough."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.5,
    "endTime": 256.7,
    "text": "Flotsam! Jetsam!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.8,
    "endTime": 262.1,
    "text": "I want you to keep an extra close watch on this pretty little daughter of his."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.2,
    "endTime": 266.5,
    "text": "She may be the key to Triton's undoing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.178,
    "endTime": 280.0,
    "text": "Hot, hot, hot, hot, hot, hot!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.9,
    "endTime": 291.9,
    "text": "Hey, Te Kā!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.2,
    "endTime": 294.7,
    "text": "Shark Head."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.4,
    "endTime": 296.9,
    "text": "Yoo-hoo!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.9,
    "endTime": 308.2,
    "text": "Moana!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 318.0,
    "endTime": 320.2,
    "text": "Get the heart to the spiral!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 342.6,
    "endTime": 347.0,
    "text": "Come on, Tiana, you're almost there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 351.4,
    "endTime": 353.7,
    "text": "My daddy never did get what he wanted."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 358.6,
    "endTime": 360.20000000000005,
    "text": "But he had what he needed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 361.0,
    "endTime": 362.6,
    "text": "He had love."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 362.7,
    "endTime": 364.9,
    "text": "He never lost sight of what was really important."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 365.0,
    "endTime": 366.2,
    "text": "Easy with that; careful!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 366.3,
    "endTime": 368.40000000000003,
    "text": "And neither will I!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 376.0,
    "endTime": 378.2,
    "text": "Y'all should've taken my deal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 378.8,
    "endTime": 383.5,
    "text": "Now you will spend the rest of your life being a slimy little frog!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 383.6,
    "endTime": 386.40000000000003,
    "text": "It's not slime; it's mucus!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 389.3,
    "endTime": 391.5,
    "text": "No, no!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 394.0,
    "endTime": 396.0,
    "text": "How am I ever gonna pay back my debt?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 398.7,
    "endTime": 400.3,
    "text": "Friends!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 400.4,
    "endTime": 402.09999999999997,
    "text": "♪ Are you ready?♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 402.2,
    "endTime": 406.09999999999997,
    "text": "No! I'm not ready at all! In fact, I got lots more plans!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 406.1,
    "endTime": 407.5,
    "text": "♪ Are you ready ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 407.6,
    "endTime": 410.5,
    "text": "This is just a minor setback in a major operation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 411.3,
    "endTime": 414.5,
    "text": "(As) Soon as I whip up another spell, we'll be back in business!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 414.6,
    "endTime": 417.6,
    "text": "I still got that froggy prince locked away!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 417.7,
    "endTime": 419.2,
    "text": "I just need a little more time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 421.1,
    "endTime": 422.70000000000005,
    "text": "No, no. Please, no!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 424.4,
    "endTime": 426.5,
    "text": "Just a little more time!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 428.3,
    "endTime": 431.1,
    "text": "I promise I'll pay y'all back! I promise!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 436.9,
    "endTime": 438.4,
    "text": "The black of night."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 441.9,
    "endTime": 446.5,
    "text": "To age my voice, an old hag's cackle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 454.2,
    "endTime": 458.3,
    "text": "To whiten my hair, a scream of fright."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 462.3,
    "endTime": 468.7,
    "text": "A blast of wind to fan my hate!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 469.7,
    "endTime": 475.7,
    "text": "A thunderbolt to mix it well."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 477.5,
    "endTime": 482.6,
    "text": "Now, begin thy magic spell."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 506.3,
    "endTime": 507.3,
    "text": "Look!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 508.5,
    "endTime": 509.9,
    "text": "My hands!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 515.9,
    "endTime": 517.0,
    "text": "My voice!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 519.2,
    "endTime": 520.2,
    "text": "My voice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 524.6,
    "endTime": 527.9,
    "text": "A perfect disguise."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 544.6,
    "endTime": 546.7,
    "text": "- On the roof!  - Look!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 563.6,
    "endTime": 566.3000000000001,
    "text": "It looks like you're out of ideas."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 569.4,
    "endTime": 571.1999999999999,
    "text": "Not quite."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 571.3,
    "endTime": 572.5,
    "text": "Ready, Mushu?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 573.4,
    "endTime": 575.1,
    "text": "I am ready, baby!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 576.1,
    "endTime": 577.2,
    "text": "Light me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 591.903,
    "endTime": 594.2,
    "text": "Get off the roof, get off the roof, get off the roof!"
  }
]